source(output(
		SYND_ID as decimal(38,18),
		SYND_NAME as string,
		CREATED_BY as string,
		CREATED_WHEN as timestamp,
		UPDATED_BY as string,
		UPDATED_WHEN as timestamp
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> syn
source(output(
		SOURCE_CODE_KEY as string,
		SOURCE_SYSTEM as string,
		TARGET_CODE as string,
		TARGET_DESCRIPTION as string,
		CODE_TYPE as string,
		CODE_TYPE_ID as double,
		CODE2 as string,
		OM_X_REF as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> tcross
tcross filter(SOURCE_SYSTEM == 'GIC' && CODE_TYPE_ID ==792) ~> Filter1
emp select(mapColumn(
		EMP_ID,
		SYND_ID
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> emp1
DerivedColumn3 select(mapColumn(
		EMPLOYEE_ID_MAIN_ADJUSTER
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> inc1
DerivedColumn4 select(mapColumn(
		SYND_ID,
		SYND_NAME
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> syn1
DerivedColumn2, inc1 join(EMP_ID == EMPLOYEE_ID_MAIN_ADJUSTER,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'none')~> Join1
Join1, syn1 join(DerivedColumn2@SYND_ID == syn1@SYND_ID,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'none')~> Join2
Join2, Filter1 join(toString(syn1@SYND_ID) == SOURCE_CODE_KEY,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'none')~> Join3
Join3 select(mapColumn(
		EMP_ID,
		SYND_ID = syn1@SYND_ID,
		SYND_NAME,
		TARGET_CODE,
		TARGET_DESCRIPTION
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Select1
Select1 aggregate(groupBy(TARGET_CODE,
		TARGET_DESCRIPTION,
		SYND_ID,
		EMP_ID),
	SYND_NAME = first(SYND_NAME)) ~> dedup
dedup derive(TEM_KEY = case(isNull(TARGET_CODE), concat('C', toString(SYND_ID)), TARGET_CODE),
		PK_PRE_DIM_CLAIM_TEAM = concat('G', toString(EMP_ID)),
		TEM_DESCRIPTION = case(isNull(TARGET_DESCRIPTION), SYND_NAME, TARGET_DESCRIPTION),
		DATE_INSERTED = currentTimestamp(),
		DATE_LAST_UPDATED = currentTimestamp(),
		INSERTED_BY = 'M_PRE_DIM_CLAIM_TEAM',
		LAST_UPDATED_BY = 'M_PRE_DIM_CLAIM_TEAM') ~> DerivedColumn1
DerivedColumn1 select(mapColumn(
		EMP_ID,
		TEM_KEY,
		PK_PRE_DIM_CLAIM_TEAM,
		TEM_DESCRIPTION,
		DATE_INSERTED,
		DATE_LAST_UPDATED,
		INSERTED_BY,
		LAST_UPDATED_BY
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Select2
emp1 derive(EMP_ID = toInteger(EMP_ID),
		SYND_ID = toInteger(SYND_ID)) ~> DerivedColumn2
inc derive(EMPLOYEE_ID_MAIN_ADJUSTER = toInteger(EMPLOYEE_ID_MAIN_ADJUSTER)) ~> DerivedColumn3
syn derive(SYND_ID = toInteger(SYND_ID)) ~> DerivedColumn4
